lasses</span> i odećom uopšte.</p>"},{"answer":"glasses","feedback":"<p>Par sočiva u okulu. Nosite ih ispred očiju kako biste bolje videli ako stvari izgledaju zamućeno.</p>"}]},"inputType":null,"tests":[],"transcript":null,"scene":{"setup":{"background":"company2-center.png","characters":[{"character":"Sophie","position":{"x":50,"y":0,"z":1.4},"opacity":0}],"audio":{"filename":"4.3-2.mp3","startTime":1,"startTimestamp":18.04,"finishTimestamp":20.68},"alwaysShowDialogue":null},"commands":[{"background":null,"character":"Sophie","position":null,"opacity":1,"startTime":0,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"character":"Sophie","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":1,"finishTime":3.64,"dialogue":{"text":"He's got long dark hair and does not wear glasses.","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Sophie","position":null,"opacity":0,"startTime":4.14,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null}]},"translationPending":false}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/#learn-how-to-clarify-information-in-different-interactions","dashedName":"task-30","certification":"a2-english-for-developers","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"a2-english-for-developers","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"learn-how-to-clarify-information-in-different-interactions","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-clarify-information-in-different-interactions/task-31","prevChallengePath":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-clarify-information-in-different-interactions/task-29","id":"663a4fa7a15067b0c128cb01","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":22,"challengeFiles":[]}},"id":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-clarify-information-in-different-interactions/task-30"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}